"# GST Classification Analysis

**Transaction:** Office supplies purchase from Officeworks - $234.67

**GST Classification:** Taxable Supply (GST-Taxable at 10%)

**Reasoning:**

- Office supplies are standard-rated goods under Australian GST legislation and are subject to the standard 10% GST rate
- Officeworks is a registered retailer of general office products and consumables, which are universally treated as taxable supplies
- The purchase does not fall within any GST exemptions (such as food, health services, education, or financial services)
- Unless the purchasing entity is GST-exempt (such as certain non-profit organizations), the full 10% GST would apply to this transaction
- The displayed price of $234.67 may be inclusive or exclusive of GST depending on the retailer's pricing policy, but the supply itself is clearly taxable

**Confidence Score:** 0.98

**Note:** The confidence is very high as office supplies are unambiguously taxable goods under Australian GST law, with no reasonable exemptions applying to this category of standard commercial goods."
